methods.add:
Add a new Series.

:param type: (io.deephaven.plot.SeriesCollection.SeriesType) - type of series
:param isMultiSeries: (boolean) - true for multi-series; false for standard mono-series.
:param series: (io.deephaven.plot.SeriesInternal) - series
methods.copy:
Creates a copy of this series collection on a new set of axes.

:param axes: (io.deephaven.plot.AxesImpl) - axes to create a copy of this series on.
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.SeriesCollection) copy of the series collection on the new set of axes.
methods.getSeriesDescriptions:
Gets the descriptions of the series in the collection. The result is a map between series name and description.

:return: (java.util.Map<java.lang.Comparable,io.deephaven.plot.SeriesCollection.SeriesDescription>) descriptions of the series in the collection
methods.remove:
Removes the series with the specified names.

:param names: (java.lang.Comparable...) - series names
methods.series:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

Gets the series with the given series ID.

*Overload 1*  
  :param id: (int) - series id
  :return: (io.deephaven.plot.SeriesInternal) series
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param name: (java.lang.Comparable) - series name
  :return: (io.deephaven.plot.SeriesInternal) series
